rows.label: bf02260100_0010
rows.name:
Nia and Byakko, executed... It
doesn't bear thinking about!

rows.label: bf02260100_0020
rows.name:
But getting aboard that
warship will be no mean feat.

rows.label: bf02260100_0030
rows.name: We're going to need an ironclad plan.

rows.label: bf02260100_0040
rows.name: Army port is under heavy guard...

rows.label: bf02260100_0050
rows.name:
I guess we'll just have to
mount a manly frontal at-

rows.label: bf02260100_0060
rows.name:
No, Rex! We can't put
everyone in danger.

rows.label: bf02260100_0090
rows.name:
This is one of the
Grandarbor's roots, right?

rows.label: bf02260100_0100
rows.name:
If this map is correct, it goes all the way
from the quay to the hull of the warship.

rows.label: bf02260100_0110
rows.name:
And here. It looks like some kind of cargo
entrance. Could we sneak on that way?

rows.label: bf02260100_0120
rows.name:
Oh, right! No one'll spot us
if we sneak in from below!

rows.label: bf02260100_0130
rows.name:
Security light around this entrance.
At night, not even workers here.

rows.label: bf02260100_0140
rows.name: Looks like this is our only option.

rows.label: bf02260100_0180
rows.name: Tora have something to show you.
